main event: An observer reported seeing an unidentified object flying between them and the moon at a high altitude on February 12, 1962.
interesting points: The sighting occurred while the observer was looking at the moon through a scope,The object was observed moving from south to north at a 25-degree angle,The object resembled a plane but did not have any lights,The observer expressed uncertainty about the object's identity,The case was listed as insufficient data due to the observer's uncertainty.
sighted object: a fast-moving object near the moon
witness description: The observer described the object as similar to a jet plane but uncertain of its true nature.
